ral estimate. It is somewhere inside the confidence interval. The bounds of the confidence interval are called the low and the high estimate. https://www.greenpeace.org/static/planet4-southeastasia-stateless/2020/02/29e450ab-data-driven-media-briefing-110220.pdf These figures are central estimates. See footnote 60 for a definition of central estimates. https://www.greenpeace.org/static/planet4-southeastasia-stateless/2020/02/21b480fa-toxic-air-report-110220.pdf https://www.unescap.org/sites/default/files/The%20Economics%20of%20Climate%20Change%20%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.pdf (Section on Highlights, page v) https://mitsloan.mit.edu/ideas-made-to-matter/psychological-economic-and-social-costs-air-pollution https://mitsloan.mit.edu/ideas-made-to-matter/psychological-economic-and-social-costs-air-pollution https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/air-pollution-and-child-health#:~:text=Globally%2C%2093%25%20of%20all%20children,indirectly%20 related%20to%20environmental%20risks.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a114d59f-e918-484b-839c-4e012a08260e": {"__data__": {"id_": "a114d59f-e918-484b-839c-4e012a08260e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-focus-clean-air-and-business-and-human-rights-agenda", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia in Focus: Clean Air and the Business and Human Rights Agenda", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-focus-clean-air-and-business-and-human-rights-agenda", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report